# ── Binary files (BANNED from version control) ───────────────────────────
# HuggingFace Spaces' pre-receive hook rejects binary files over git and
# requires Xet LFS storage instead (https://huggingface.co/docs/hub/xet).
# Rather than maintain a Xet pipeline, this project keeps the repo text-
# only and regenerates or downloads any binary artifacts on demand.
# If you genuinely need a binary at runtime, fetch it in the Dockerfile
# or at app start-up — do NOT commit it.

